{"tid":370265,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"舒利亞叫盧卡古：咪聽亨利講！","createTime":"2017-08-23T02:11:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-26T16:50:17.000Z","uid":8968,"like":35,"dislike":211,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"807d9caf3e66de280917c6e44288c7641c4d12af","tid":370265,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T02:11:35.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=APckT7yvosIwZc4AGUGEJRxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=798f9e5c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】前鋒盧卡古加盟曼聯後，在2場英超轟入3球，表現非凡，更引起2大英超傳奇射手亨利和舒利亞爭論。<br />\n<br />\n前阿仙奴射手亨利（Thierry Henry）早前<span style=\"color: red;\">批評盧卡古（Romelu Lukaku）的走位和控球，認為他應該更多主動走位，令自己身處更好的接應位置，也為隊友提供更多傳球選擇。</span><br />\n<br />\n不過，前紐卡素兼英格蘭隊長舒利亞（Alan Shearer）近日就大唱反調，更認為如果盧卡古聽取亨利的意見，只會令自己失去最強一環。舒利亞表示：「<span style=\"color: red;\">有人批評他的串連工作做得不好，但他不是這種球員，是一名入球者，要在禁區附近。任何指射手要墮後做串連的說法，我都不同意</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n舒利亞又指，「紅魔」陣中已經有很多創造型球員，盧卡古這位9號仔只需做好入球的本份：「<span style=\"color: red;\">曼聯有足夠的創造力，前場有速度和活力，而且他們已有足夠信心去突破</span>。」<br />\n<br />\n🤔🤔🤔🤔🤔<br />\n亨利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n舒利亞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"495a37a851f9a9f5af7251c5caf667a3a43f7945","tid":370265,"uid":16767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T02:12:59.000Z","msg":"撐老舒"},{"pid":"e39e6f9821431d2811dabc938e31e870b41f4649","tid":370265,"uid":51453,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T02:13:23.000Z","msg":"亨利有陰謀"},{"pid":"d2fd3753168b5a66c7edeaee9ec4f9b81af24b32","tid":370265,"uid":60569,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T02:19:21.000Z","msg":"佢兩個好似講返球員時代既自己咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed2b79b47f341331580d583f3cf58562212a441","tid":370265,"uid":52876,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-23T02:23:31.000Z","msg":"最強9號賓斯馬笑而不